Variables

===^_^===> depending on what's stored inside a container

---> pure value or address of an object
	----> primitive variable
	----> reference variable

===^_^===> depending on where the variable defined at

---> inside a method
    ----> called local variable
    
---> if it's on method decleration 
	----> called method parameters
	
---> if it's outside any method under the class
	----> field
		-----> instance field/variable
		-----> static field / variable
===^_^===>